    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="writingSession">
                <opener><dateline><pb/>
                        <hi rendition="#mPrint">6, Essex Street. Manchester</hi>. <lb/>21 Feb.
                        1867.</dateline><salute>Dear Engels,</salute></opener>
                <p>Half a dozen bachelors have been asked to dine with me
                    on <seg type="comment"><orig>Thursday next</orig><note xml:id="dffa8aa2-9b5d-4c8d-a90e-4963a3f72a5c">28. Februar
                            1867.</note></seg>
                    <?oxy_comment_start author="lindenberg" timestamp="20180612T123335+0200" comment="vorher: 26. Februar 1867"?>at<?oxy_comment_end?> 5.
                    In mufti not in dinner togs. Will you come also?</p>
                <closer>Yours very truly<lb/>Isaac Hall.</closer>
                <p>F Engels Esq<hi rendition="#sup">r</hi>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
